Coming to our conversation events is very economical, from only 3 per individual event or if you prefer the annual fee of 70 or 100 for couples with which you can come to all the events and have discounts on other activities such as cooking classes, in addition to being able to participate in competitions.


Plus, if you bring a friend to join us as an annual member, you get 10 and your friend gets a 10 discount on the annual rate.


Every day is different at conversation events. We propose different themes and role-playing games so that you can put into practice everything learned in grammar classes and achieve the fluency you want by acquiring new vocabulary.


Conversation events are not classes but they are an excellent way to deepen the conversation, which is what is most difficult in all languages and they are also an ideal complement if you are attending classes or have attended in the past and want to continue practicing your Spanish .

The ideal is to have a minimum A2 level to be able to follow the conversations.


If you want to take some classes beforehand, each individual class personalized to your needs costs 30 and the A1 level courses start in September and are 8 weeks for 250.


Below you can book the days you want to attend an event, keep in mind that you can reserve up to 3 hours before the day you want to attend the event.

Please book only if you are 100% sure to attend as there will be other people waiting for you.
